1. Molim vas, da li pružate *usluge* prevoza? (Please, do you provide transportation *services*?)
2. Naša firma se bavi pružanjem *usluga* čišćenja. (Our company is engaged in providing *cleaning services*.)
3. Da li ste zadovoljni *uslugom* koju ste dobili? (Are you satisfied with the *service* you received?)
4. Ovaj hotel ima odlične *usluge* restorana. (This hotel has excellent *restaurant services*.)
5. Usluga *dostave* je besplatna za porudžbine preko 1000 dinara. (The *delivery service* is free for orders over 1000 dinars.)
6. Da li ste ikada koristili *usluge* ovog frizera? (Have you ever used the *services* of this hairdresser?)
7. Usluga *popravke* automobila je vrlo skupa. (The *car repair service* is very expensive.)
8. Naša firma nudi *usluge* savetovanja za male preduzetnike. (Our company offers *consulting services* for small business owners.)
9. Kada je gužva, *usluge* taksija mogu biti spore. (When it's crowded, *taxi services* can be slow.)
10. Ovaj restoran je poznat po izvrsnoj *usluzi* i hrani. (This restaurant is known for its excellent *service* and food.)